      <h3>What we do</h3>
      <p>CF PharmTech was founded in 2007, it is a fully independent, dynamic, integrated, specialty pharmaceutical company focused on the development and manufacturing of products for the treatments of asthma, COPD and allergic rhinitis for the global market. Its mission is to develop high-quality and affordable medicine to help patients achieve effective management care for their respiratory diseases.</p>
      <p>The headquarters is located in the lakeside of the Caohu District of Suzhou, Jiangsu Province, with many very convenient transportation options available. It is only thirty minutes by train to Shanghai and four hours by train to Beijing.</p>
      <p>The company was founded by a top caliber team consisting of veterans from both the American and Chinese pharmaceutical industries. The venture was sponsored by the leading Chinese public pharmaceutical company, numerous healthcare venture funds, and Wuxi 530 seed investment program.</p>
      <p>Cutting-edge technology enables CF Pharmtech to develop pharmaceutical products that meet the increasing need of the worldwide market. The company has established state-of-the-art manufacturing lines for MDI, dry powder inhaler (DPI), nebulizer, and nasal spray.</p>
      <p>CF considers developing therapies to help patients with airway-related diseases as one of its most significant impacts. With the philosophy of “breathe easy,” CF PharmTech is becoming bigger and stronger in respiratory therapy.</p>
