      <h3>Our Logo</h3>
      <p>CF’s identity represents its commitment to provide safe and high-quality medicine to help patients achieve effective management care for their chronic respiratory diseases.</p>
      <p>The name CF comes from an old Chinese Poem, “Chang Feng Po Lang”, meaning hope and renewal.</p>
      <p>The logo incorporates the company name “CF”. It is an abstract image of the respiratory tract, illustrating the company’s focus on the respiratory area. The hexagon represents rationality, science, and professionalism and as a symbol of chemistry, represents the pharmaceutical industry. Blue is for reliability and tranquility and the “F” is a symbol of a sailboat which shows exploration, innovation, and discovery. </p>
